At this point, I've thoroughly explored the code and the CLI seems to work correctly. But the bug report says it doesn't work. Let me think about what other aspect could be broken...

Wait, let me look at `match_to_lint` line 45 more carefully:

```rust
let word = &matched_tokens[0];

